%N A157106 a(n) = 5651522*n^2 - 2541672*n + 285769.
%C A157106 The identity (5651522*n^2 - 2541672*n + 285769)^2 - (1681*n^2 - 756*n + 85)*(137842*n - 30996)^2 = 1 can be written as a(n)^2 - A157010(n)*A157105(n)^2 = 1.
